{"tid":782083,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（無事啦）中國商務部副部長率團赴美磋商經貿問題","createTime":"2018-08-16T12:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T00:24:46.000Z","uid":147097,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a91ed5410044736d932fb2cac3f1d87e30280b65","tid":782083,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"中國商務部表示，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">應美方邀請</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">商務部副部長</span></span>兼國際貿易談判副代表王受文擬於8月下旬率團訪美，與美國財政部副部長馬爾帕斯(David Malpass)率領的美方代表團就雙方各自關注的中美經貿問題進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n商務部稱，中方重申，反對單邊主義和貿易保護主義做法，不接受任何單邊貿易限制措施。中方歡迎在對等、平等、誠信的基礎上，開展對話和溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3152ed007c7287014a4e88941dd7a3f64aff89a5","tid":782083,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:07:50.000Z","msg":"不如搵個城管過去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e15dcb5342683fa66d2bbdfb7e506b5cbd1dfe","tid":782083,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T22:51:25.000Z","msg":"搵個副的，幾明顯仲係試水溫"},{"pid":"7b6cd87dd6f97396664d257bc7fb740876b585c1","tid":782083,"uid":37599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T23:19:26.000Z","msg":"侵侵想撚狗咪叫你過黎hand hand,  等睇玻璃心嬲嬲豬反檯，之後侵侵又再扣佢50分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3944e02b732dc6210a524d9fc9e8044803242e1f","tid":782083,"uid":60376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"應美方邀請，即係中方請求<br />\n搵副部長去，即係想低調談判<br />\n應該都係跪低多"},{"pid":"1c2e3d252ca21e207c92214424d523377fa5a14f","tid":782083,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3944e02b732dc6210a524d9fc9e8044803242e1f","tid":782083,"uid":60376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T23:28:09.000Z","m